      "name": "ASTM F1717 compression-bending operating envelope for 7.5 mm non-cannulated pedicle screw",
      "description": "Screw outer diameter: 7.5 mm ± 0.05 mm; screw length: 40–55 mm; titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V ELI, UTS 860–930 MPa); ASTM F1717 test block spacing: 35–45 mm; applied axial compressive load: 0–4000 N; crosshead displacement rate: 5 mm/min ± 0.5 mm/min; ambient temperature: 20–25 °C; rod diameter: 5.5 mm; construct tested to 40 mm displacement or structural failure, whichever occurs first."
    },
