      "description": "Model applicability is restricted to non-cannulated Ti-6Al-4V ELI pedicle screws of 7.5 mm nominal outer diameter tested under ASTM F1717 static compression-bending protocol. Cannulated variants, polyaxial screw heads, dynamic stabilization rods, fatigue loading, and in vivo bone-implant interface conditions are explicitly outside the validated envelope. Extrapolation to screw diameters outside 7.0–8.0 mm requires additional validation evidence."
    }
